    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied at all evaluated operating points. The overall evidence package supports regulatory submission.",
